                    <li class="room-list" id="extra-padding"><img src="https://img.icons8.com/material-rounded/26/000000/landscape.png"/> Vue sur le Mont Mezenc</li>
                    
                    <li class="room-list" id="extra-padding"><img src="https://img.icons8.com/android/26/000000/wifi.png"/> Wifi gratuit</li>
                    
